<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"> <channel><title>Hiraeth&#39;s Wiki</title><description>My personal wiki</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/</link><atom:link href="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" /><managingEditor>hiraeth</managingEditor><docs>https://github.com/hiraethecho/wiki</docs><language>en</language> <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 06:58:02 -0000</pubDate> <lastBuildDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 06:58:02 -0000</lastBuildDate> <ttl>1440</ttl> <generator>MkDocs RSS plugin - v1.16.0</generator> <item> <title>About</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;My online wiki&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;I&#39;m using zotero, obsidian and mkdocs to create a wiki.This is the mkdocs part of it, and is hosted by github pages.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;!-- - [About](/wiki/...&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:54:01 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/</guid> </item> <item> <title>This is my Notes about computer</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;This is my Notes about computer&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Concludes linux, software, latex, etc&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;linux and code&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/wiki/code/archinstall&#34;&gt;install arch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[git note](/wiki/code/...&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:54:01 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/</guid> </item> <item> <title>用mkdocs、obsidian、zotero搭建个人wiki</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;使用mkdocs、obsidian、zotero搭建个人在线wiki&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;工作流是，在zotero中阅读和标记。用zotero-better-notes插件把标记变成文本格式，并且导出到obsidian的库文件中，进一步编辑（或者用nvim编辑）。在obsidian中更方便笔记链接跳转，zotero只是文献管理和...&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/3in1wiki/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:54:01 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/3in1wiki/</guid> </item> <item> <title>双系统安装archlinux</title> <category>arch</category> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Basic installation of arch linux&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;双系统安装archlinux，使用btrfs文件系统。重装系统的个人参考。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;启动盘&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;下载archlinux的iso文件。找一个U盘，用 &lt;code&gt;ventoy&lt;/code&gt;安装，然后把iso放进去。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;可以先在win下用 &lt;kbd&gt;win&lt;/kbd&gt;+...&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/archinstall/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:54:01 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/archinstall/</guid> </item> <item> <title>Tips for archlinux</title> <category>arch</category> <description>&lt;h2&gt;sh&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;后台挂起&lt;code&gt;shnohup onedrivegui &amp;amp; &amp;gt; /dev/null&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;configuration&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;net&lt;/strong&gt;Using iwd as backend of NetworkManager:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;/etc/NetworkManager/NetworkManager.co...&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/archtips/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:54:01 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/archtips/</guid> </item> <item> <title>用btrfs做linux的快照备份</title> <category>arch</category> <description>&lt;h1&gt;btrfs 的备份&lt;/h1&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/bt