pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/nvim/</guid> </item> <item> <title>obsidian</title> <category>obsidian</category> <description>&lt;h1&gt;obsidian&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Install&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;plugins&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;dataview&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;kanban&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Hover Editor&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/obsidian/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:54:01 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/obsidian/</guid> </item> <item> <title>zotero</title> <category>obsidian</category> <category>wiki</category> <category>zotero</category> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Zotero&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Install and basic setting&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Plugins&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;zotero 7:&lt;/strong&gt;- zotmoov- zotero better notes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Sync&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;using ~~zotmoov~~ attanger to move files&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;zotero ...&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/zotero/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:54:01 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/zotero/</guid> </item> <item> <title>Life Hacker!</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Life Hacker!&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;这里是一些关于“如何生活”的笔记。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;活着太tm累了，找到改善游戏难度的作弊码，或者发现舒适圈小游戏，当然应该记下来啦。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/wiki/life/cocktail&#34;&gt;喝酒！&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/life/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:54:01 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/life/</guid> </item> <item> <title>cocktail</title> <category>alcohol</category> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Cocktail&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;!!! tip &lt;strong&gt;Drink properly&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;关于鸡尾酒的小知识&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;理论部分&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;《鸡尾酒法典》将所有调酒分为6个框架，即所有无论是多么花里胡哨的酒都是建立在该种基础上的。1. &lt;code&gt;old fashioned&lt;/code&gt; 即古典类鸡尾酒，这个古典鸡尾酒曾是所有鸡尾酒的代名词，在19世纪初鸡...&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/life/cocktail/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:54:01 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/life/cocktail/</guid> </item> <item> <title>My math Notes</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;My math Notes&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mainly Algebraic Geometry&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Basic AG&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hartshorne, EGA, etc&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Birational Geomatry&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Pre BCHM&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;KM98&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;BCHM&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;bchm&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Post BCHM&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;bir12.Non-Q-...&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:54:01 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/</guid> </item> <item> <title>BCHM</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;BCHM&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2&gt;PreBCHM&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;including KM98&lt;br&gt; we can run mmp for klt Q-factorial pairs, except existence of flip.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;BCHM&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;MMP for $(X,B)$ klt and $B$ big&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;PostBCH...&lt;/h2&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/BCHM/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:54:01 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/BCHM/</guid> </item> <item> <title>Introduction to MMP</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;MMP&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;In this class, we consider normal varities over $\mathbb{C}$.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Intro&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our goal is to classify algebraic varieties up to birational equivalence, the...&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/BCHM/intro/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:54:01 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/BCHM/intro/</guid> </item> <item> <title>Topics in Moduli</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Moduli spaces&lt;/h1&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/Moduli/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:54:01 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/Moduli/</guid> </item> <item> <title>2</title> <description>&lt;h2&gt;rationality&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;$rational \subset unirational \subset rationally connected \subset uniruled$&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;where &lt;em&gt;uniruled&lt;/em&gt; if $\mathbb{P}^1\times Y \dashrightarrow X$ do...&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/Seminars/2/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:54:01 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/Seminars/2/</guid> </item> <item> <title>817_10-11</title> <description>&lt;h2&gt;Tangent space of $\mathrm{Mor}(Y,X)$&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Goal: proof that&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;$$ T_{Mor(Y,x),[f]} \cong H^0(Y,\mathcal{H}om(f^*\Omega _X,\mathcal{O}_Y) $$&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;dimension of tang...&lt;/h2&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/Seminars/817_10-11/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:54:01 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/Seminars/817_10-11/</guid> </item> <item> <title>1</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Seminar&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Plan&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Part I&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;parametrizing morphisms (&#34;Bend-and-break&#34; producing rational curves)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unirules and Ratinally connected varieties (&#34;smoothi...&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/Seminars/birational_seminar/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:54:01 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_updated.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/Seminars/birational_seminar/</guid> </item> </channel></rss>